function setMap(n) {
    if(n==0) {
        TileEngine.setColorMap(COLOR_MAPA)
        document.getElementById('btm0').className = "btn btn-primary"
        document.getElementById('btm1').className = "btn btn-light"
    } else {
        TileEngine.setColorMap(COLOR_MAPB)
        document.getElementById('btm0').className = "btn btn-light"
        document.getElementById('btm1').className = "btn btn-primary"
    }
    Canvas.redrawGraphics()
}
